From Dan Sorenson Subject Re Why I wanted police officers to answer my posting Charles Sundheim writes Some potentially cool story stuff Do share the HOW TO GET A VERBAL WARNING FOR IN A It's First it has to be the first really nice riding day of The bike is back together again and so are Grab all your gear put it on and fill the tank with octane premium or Head In Ames there is a road that leads to the little town of Gilbert has one stop light if that tells you Having just gotten the bike back together I thought I'd take it for a short ride and check things Heading out of town I went into the twisties at a slow pace just under the speed limit and started leaning The pace quickened as everything felt just Finally the road straightened and I was ready for a bit of Grab third gear open her At roughly grab fourth Look at as much of the bike as you can and fail to notice a state trooper following a quarter mile Twist the throttle like a fool grab fifth gear at or so and see just how well she's been put back At according to radar I noticed the front fender was flexing a Thus I slowed pulled off the road removed my helmet and gloves unslung the took kit I was carrying in a fanny pack and was just starting to tighten that fender when the trooper pulled in all hot and Have you ANY idea how fast you were going Not precisely I was paying attention to the bike and road not the I just got her back together last night and I'm just out here testing her out before I ride it in My radar says you were at over Care to tell me why I shouldn't give you a ticket Because I was testing the motorcycle away from population and traffic on a strait and flat road while wearing all the protective gear that safety demands note I wasn't quite that eloquent Say what kind of bike is that anyway I was eloquent on my cafe racer replica Honda a Rat Bike Yeah I haven't had my bike out of the garage in compare riding stories pack toolkit having tightened that fender So why were you out here I figure every other idiot on the road is going to look right through If the bike fails somehow in a zone I'm If it holds up out here then I know it will work right in I do this evvery year when I rebuild Not any You'll find a better place than my highway to do those If I ever catch you speeding on my highway again I'm going to nail you for everything I possibly Now get out of my sight before I write you a Yes And kid keep your eyes open out drives off And that in a nut shell is how to get a warning for in a I don't guarantee that it will work for you but it worked for Dan Sorenson DoD ISU only censors what I read not what I Don't blame USENET Post to exotic distant Meet exciting unusual And flame